  "sn22.127:1.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22",
  "sn22.127:2.1": "13. Avijjāvagga",
  "sn22.127:3.1": "127. Dutiyasamudayadhammasutta",
  "sn22.127:4.1": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca mahākoṭṭhiko bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye.",
  "sn22.127:4.2": "Atha kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito … pe …",
  "sn22.127:4.3": "ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:",
  "sn22.127:4.4": "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati.",
  "sn22.127:4.5": "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, avijjā;",
  "sn22.127:4.6": "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti?",
  "sn22.127:5.1": "“Idhāvuso assutavā puthujjano samudayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti;",
  "sn22.127:5.2": "vayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ … pe …",
  "sn22.127:5.3": "‘samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti.",
  "sn22.127:5.4": "Samudayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ … pe …",
  "sn22.127:5.5": "vayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ … pe …",
  "sn22.127:5.6": "‘samudayavayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti.",
  "sn22.127:5.7": "Samudayadhammaṃ saññaṃ … pe …",
  "sn22.127:5.8": "samudayadhamme saṅkhāre … pe …",
  "sn22.127:5.9": "vayadhamme saṅkhāre … pe …",
  "sn22.127:5.10": "samudayavayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayavayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti.",
  "sn22.127:5.11": "Samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ … pe …",
  "sn22.127:5.12": "samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti.",
  "sn22.127:5.13": "Ayaṃ vuccati, āvuso, avijjā;",
  "sn22.127:5.14": "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti.",
  "sn22.127:6.1": "Dutiyaṃ."
}